+
+In Easy and hard mode, you can combine any numbers in the table to equal the goal number.
+In quiz mode, you can combine n numbers in the top-right corner which add up to equal the goal number in 20s.
+
+Tap the number in the left bottom corner, you can change the goal number to another one."</string>
